There are two different types of applications for the customer intake journey; 

For accepting paper application or electronic application New Business applications (NB) is used which includes; NB WebApp, Simple Protect, AURA, LOPA. 

These applications help in take insurance apps and determine how much insurance coverage amount can be offered, what kind of risk the customer has, once all assessment is done, insurance is issued to the customer 

When insurance is issued, customer information is passed to Policy Administration applications which include; Ingenium 5.4, Ingenium 7, IB, FM, etc. 

The Strategic direction is to merge all policy admin systems into one which is Ingenium 7. 
